Interface CubeListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MainActivity, SplashActivity, TutorialActivity

    public interface CubeListener
    Interface that has to be implemented by other classes when they want to be informed of CubeChangedEvents.

    Mario Kraml

    • Method Detail

      • cubeHasChanged

        void cubeHasChanged(CubeChangedEvent _event)
        Method that gets called when the cube has been changed. In the parameter event a Step representation of the new cube side on front of the cube is saved.
        Parameters:
        _event - A Step representation of the new cube side on front of the cube.

      • cubeHasChanged

        void cubeHasChanged(TutorialCubeChangedEvent _event)
        Method that gets called when the cube has been changed in the tutorial. In the parameter event a TutorialStep representation of the new cube side on front of the cube is saved.
        Parameters:
        _event - A TutorialStep representation of the new cube side on front of the cube.
